<field_public_text>:
This field tells the distance from the the desired previous clock edge to the actual time it was generated. Ie. an output edge is asked to be created at 12.0 ns, and the internal time of day had the value of 12.45 ns. This field will then ben set to 0.45. Format is 5.8 fixedpoint.
